<div style="font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 20px;">Password Changed</h1>

  <p>Hi <%= @user.email %>,</p>

  <p>Your password was recently changed. If you made this change, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

  <p><strong>If you did not change your password</strong>, someone may have accessed your account. Please secure your account immediately by:</p>

  <ol>
    <li>Changing your password</li>
    <li>Reviewing your recent account activity</li>
    <li>Checking for any unauthorized changes</li>
  </ol>

  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">
    This is a security notification and cannot be disabled.
  </p>
</div>
